## Sitemap limits (do not ÔÇťfixÔÇŁ without product decision)

- Up to **1000** publication URLs in sitemap (`listPublicationsPublic` limit)
- **First translated chapter** reading URL for at most **100** publications (`SITEMAP_CHAPTER_PUBS_LIMIT`)
- `/catalog` canonical on SSR points to `/` (duplicate-content control)

## When changing SEO behavior

- Update `routing.mdc` SEO section if SSR paths, disallow rules, or sitemap shape change
- Update `seo-search-console.md` or new audit note in `docs/05-plans/`
- Run verifier after `src/` edits
